						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa, Kulōttuṅga, Year 12 = c. 11th-12th Century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records that on the instructions of Kaṟkaḍamārāya Pūmināyakar, one Naṟṟa-koṟṟantai Pērāyiramuḍaiyān Ponnan of Tirumunaippāḍi made a tank in the village Kuṟichilipāri in Puṟamalai-nāḍu and gave it as <hi rend="italic">tirumaḍaippaḷḷi-puṟam</hi> of Tīrttamalai-uḍaiyār temple.</p>						

						</summary>
