<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tribhu</hi>vanac cakkaravattikaḷ
<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulottuṅka coḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku Iyā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇṭu panniraṇṭāvatu kaṟkaṭamārāya pūmi
<lb n="4"/>nāyakar coṟpaṭi tirumunaippāṭi naṟ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟa koṟṟaṉtai perāyiramuṭaiyān ponna
<lb n="6" break="no"/>neṉ puṟamalaināṭṭuk kuṟicilipāriyil Eri
<lb n="7"/>maṇalile kaḻueri En <hi rend="grantha">śari</hi>ra varuttattā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>l Uṭaiyār tirttamalai Uṭaiyāṟku
<lb n="9"/>Amutuppaṭikku tānamāka paṭalan pūminā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>yanum koṟṟantai ponnanum Āka viṭṭoṭi
<lb n="11"/>koṟṟantai ponnan kuṭiniṅkāt te<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied> tānamāka Uḻu
<lb n="12" break="no"/>tu vāramiṭak kaṭaven Itu paṉmāyecura
<lb n="13" break="no"/>i<hi rend="grantha">rakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi>
</p>

